data.description: You won't want to miss this adorable three bed, one bath home with just over 1,000 square feet of living space all on one level. The newly updated kitchen includes quartz counter tops, new appliances, light fixtures, and, of course, a farmhouse sink! The hardwoods throughout give the home a warm and inviting feel. And with amenities like a new tankless hot water heater, forced air gas heat, and central air, this home has a lot to offer and is priced to sell!
